{
  "id": "RAW_b3eed533",
  "title": "在全世界都教你写 Prompt 的时候，我做了个不用 Prompt 的 AI 画图产品",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&mid=2247499824&idx=1&sn=e05cde04151d311a2452599e386d1c04",
  "date": "2025-11-24 07:41:00",
  "author": "刘小排",
  "siteName": "刘小排r",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=84bd4cc1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F607DKnuWzlHKuuxH7LmfEThEFKY3KjLJVgPptZLolY8vtspuUfRTE1H17W7EeGRl33GPv1Gg64nYbH4KqYGXtA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p>\n   <br>\n  </p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">哈喽，大家好，我是刘小排。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">最近我做了一个新产品，叫&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">Morisot</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">简单说，它是一块</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">不会写 Prompt 也能用的 AI 画图板</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://morisot.ai\" target=\"_blank\">https://morisot.ai</a></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">产品刚刚上线，先邀请各位朋友来帮我一起打磨。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">欢迎你来玩、来挑毛病，顺手点个一键三连，感激不尽！</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);font-size:24px;\">为什么我要做Morisot这款产品？</span></span></h2>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">几年前，我在前东家做手机输入法产品。有一天，我盯着自己电脑上的输入法皮肤，突然冒出一个念头：</span></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"text-align:left;\">\n   <p><strong><span leaf=\"\">“这皮肤，我真的看腻了。”</span></strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">但紧接着第二个念头就是——</span></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"text-align:left;\">\n   <p><strong><span leaf=\"\">“那我想要什么风格呢？”</span></strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">我竟然一句话也说不清。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">「要不要换成深色？」「还是再可爱一点？」「要不要来点扁平、极简、3D科技感？」……</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">按常规做法，产品经理下一步应该是：</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">写一份很专业的需求文档，认真描述——</span></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"text-align:left;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">主色调要偏什么色号</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"text-align:left;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">视觉要偏哪个方向</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"text-align:left;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">字体要怎么样……</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">但是那一刻我非常诚实地承认：</span></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"text-align:left;\">\n   <p><strong><span leaf=\"\">我根本写不出来。</span></strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">我只知道自己「看腻了」，我并不「知道自己想要什么」。</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">最后，我们是怎么解决的呢？</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">设计部门老大直接拍板，让所有设计师先别管别的需求：「每个人做三套输入法皮肤方案，下周我们一口气看。」</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">一周之后，会议室的长桌上摆满了几十套方案。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">有极简的、赛博的、插画风的、日系小清新的……一眼看过去，像一整面「输入法皮肤展墙」。</span></p>\n  <p data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"https://sistine-tech.feishu.cn/space/api/box/stream/download/asynccode/?code=YjMzZTQwZWZhMWYwZDU3YTVmM2Q3NjBhZWQ2ZTc4NGNfVWRjdlRnQVRCeWRoaXpsTGE0dWdRaWpPbEZBSjNyREVfVG9rZW46SUI5bWJVTTBlb0VIWGR4RmdOUWN2SktEbmRZXzE3NjM5Njg4NDU6MTc2Mzk3MjQ0NV9WNA\" data-src=\"\" align=\"\" alt=\"\" border=\"\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"\" data-s=\"\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" hspace=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" style=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"\" usemap=\"\" vspace=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"1280\" data-height=\"960\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100016139\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-retry=\"\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"960\" data-imgfileid=\"100016158\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-width=\"1280\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d500db6f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHKuuxH7LmfEThEFKY3KjLJ9Qf5ecSIibwNXXNqmwKk8ab9J7Qj9pcSUHluvalveWOYmWGrru8HW1A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"960\" data-imgfileid=\"100016157\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-width=\"1280\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ae5e64dc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHKuuxH7LmfEThEFKY3KjLJfMn0V3RO45l2Y2qo5V19wu1NISCoAg4WN9QIzb4Bdm8fk4VoQ6z2yA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">（你是不是想问，照片上为什么没有我？ 呃，因为我在拍照）</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">我让设计师伙伴们一个一个讲解设计方案，产品经理参与讨论和选择。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">在讨论会上，我们只是一直在做一件事：</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">“用手指一点一点地说：这张不错，这张一般，这张完全不是。”</span></strong></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">选着选着，我突然有一种很强烈的感觉：</span></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"text-align:left;\">\n   <p><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">“原来我想要的，就大概是这几张的感觉。我们继续迭代这几张即可！”</span></span></strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">那一刻我才意识到——</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">我不是不知道自己要什么，我只是</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">没办法用语言先把它描述出来</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);font-size:24px;\">AI能画图以后，人类的创作过程有改变吗？</span></span></h2>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">到了2023年以后，我们有了AIGC，我仍然苦于写不出来图片的Prompt、画不出来好图，想必你也一样。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">想起来当年我做输入法皮肤的故事，我开始明白了：</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">AI能画图以后，人类的创作过程没有改变。</span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color:rgb(222,120,2);\"><span leaf=\"\">绝大多数创作，都不是从‘描述’开始的，是从‘看’开始的。</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color:rgb(222,120,2);\"><span leaf=\"\">人类创造不是靠 prompt，而是靠眼睛。</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color:rgb(222,120,2);\"><span leaf=\"\">I know it when I see it</span></span><span leaf=\"\">.</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">平凡的我们，创作流程应该是 ：&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:rgb(222,120,2);\"><span leaf=\"\">说不清 → 先看一墙图 → 指一指喜欢的 → 再改一改</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">这一轮 AIGC 差不多已经火了三年。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">大部分 AI 画图工具，依赖于使用者构思出精妙的 Prompt，才能画出用户心中满意的图。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">说白了，它们还是在服务「能把自己说清楚」的人。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">但我一直在想：</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">那大多数说不清的人怎么办？</span></strong></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">所以我做了 Morisot。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">一句话概括就是：</span></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"text-align:left;\">\n   <p><strong><span leaf=\"\">你可能说不清你要什么图，</span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;但你看到的时候，就知道哪张对。</span></strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">在 Morisot 里，你不需要会写 Prompt。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">你只要把一个模糊的 idea 丢进来——</span></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"text-align:left;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">比如「毛坯房想看看不同装修风格」</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"text-align:left;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">比如「深秋的北京胡同」</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"text-align:left;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">比如「多种键盘风格」</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\">十秒钟，它给你生成一墙好图。</span></strong></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">你可以先用眼睛挑：</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">哪几张是「对味的」？</span></strong></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">选中之后，再用很人话的方式，跟 AI 说：</span></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"text-align:left;\">\n   <p><span leaf=\"\">「再黄昏一点。」 &nbsp;「加一个沙发。」 &nbsp;「颜色再高级一点。」</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">它就帮你一轮轮改下去。</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016156\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6620370370370371\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2720\" data-height=\"1800\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bbf3e8f3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHKuuxH7LmfEThEFKY3KjLJz7WibCKMVZbDV7yP4tVSkbhpu0K4HsRyibANNxPs9VRVJanB3iaibFT6Ng%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">轮到 Morisot 登场了 。</span></p>\n  </h2>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);font-size:24px;\">一些Morisot的使用案例</span></span></h2>\n  <h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(120, 172, 254);font-size:18px;\">1.毛坯房变装修效果图</span></span></h3>\n  <h3 style=\"text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;heading&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h2&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:2},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">我们拍摄一张毛坯房的照片</span></h3>\n  <p data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"https://sistine-tech.feishu.cn/space/api/box/stream/download/asynccode/?code=NTU0OWEyMGI2ZDQ3ZjBjYTlhZTE1ZWUxNmI4ZTdkMTJfdXZZUzh0MEIwSDh2ZVVYVVF5bTRoQXA3cFltc1hCNWVfVG9rZW46RXlzMWJBYWdMb2Y2RWt4NDdiMWNqSHpibkp6XzE3NjM5Njg4NDU6MTc2Mzk3MjQ0NV9WNA\" data-src=\"\" align=\"\" alt=\"\" border=\"\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"\" data-s=\"\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" hspace=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" style=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"\" usemap=\"\" vspace=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"3374\" data-height=\"1760\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100016152\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-retry=\"\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"378\" data-imgfileid=\"100016155\" data-ratio=\"0.7132075471698113\" data-width=\"530\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"530\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c341e4a7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHKuuxH7LmfEThEFKY3KjLJsUxfqUibwPtl8YBhL0LuVPGicGJj8sZiczg125aAPlgFsicLg6zNZ70WpQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">输入要求：“改成不同风格的装修效果”</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">就能得到下面这一墙</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016159\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5212962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"3374\" data-height=\"1760\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b6b0bfb4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHKuuxH7LmfEThEFKY3KjLJLzxK59DUSRiaiaq2Fe0KbNbXQOYPtL0h01C4LkRLXLkM4CjEXOwr20XQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">我们可以选中图片，进行二次编辑。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">比如，我想看看某张图黄昏时分的样子 （中英文输入均可）</span></p>\n  <pre><code data-lark-language=\"JSON\" data-wrap=\"true\"><p><span leaf=\"\">make it look like sunset time</span></p></code></pre>\n  <p data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"https://sistine-tech.feishu.cn/space/api/box/stream/download/asynccode/?code=MDUxYzdjZGU4ZWQ0NTM1ODAzOTMwNjVlNzVmMDcwMjdfVGQ2ZnptNmtYWDlDN25WR1dMbGxYMGlpR0hqMmw1TU9fVG9rZW46VzlmMmJyVFM1b3AwR3h4azZJTGNsYndPbjZkXzE3NjM5Njg4NDU6MTc2Mzk3MjQ0NV9WNA\" data-src=\"\" align=\"\" alt=\"\" border=\"\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"\" data-s=\"\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" hspace=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" style=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"\" usemap=\"\" vspace=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"3368\" data-height=\"1752\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100016142\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-retry=\"\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016162\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5222222222222223\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"3376\" data-height=\"1764\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=521ac15f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHKuuxH7LmfEThEFKY3KjLJLibdLycSLibTDO47DhKkxqEku9NibMnU5TQVyfJQqhSuhVBXYZlt3OO8g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016163\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5203703703703704\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"3368\" data-height=\"1752\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e1b9b781&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHKuuxH7LmfEThEFKY3KjLJL4jKoE8HdvicPEzBkDibgs3wssKZHAcY0q9wvicz41f3gYIK72QicYWZOg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">纯用文字，想怎么改怎么改。我们加上沙发试试</span></p>\n  <p data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"https://sistine-tech.feishu.cn/space/api/box/stream/download/asynccode/?code=YjZmZGQ5NmQ0NTQ1OTIyZTViOTJiZTBiODI0Y2VjZWFfNWxUdXl4cDlsTUE4UzFxREhXWHJXNFRiZXZZdTNRNnJfVG9rZW46UUxiZ2JWalhxb05XTkJ4Um92OWNvbUN5bk1oXzE3NjM5Njg4NDU6MTc2Mzk3MjQ0NV9WNA\" data-src=\"\" align=\"\" alt=\"\" border=\"\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"\" data-s=\"\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" hspace=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" style=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"\" usemap=\"\" vspace=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"3384\" data-height=\"1750\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100016153\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"1\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-retry=\"\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"1734\" data-imgfileid=\"100016161\" data-ratio=\"0.5185185185185185\" data-width=\"3346\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6c31508a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHKuuxH7LmfEThEFKY3KjLJTHblu8BAx7mq7SpG7vzf4gKCmV9o5qgJ2K5YHSBWQugYM6z3C6yy7w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016165\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5175925925925926\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"3384\" data-height=\"1750\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=58b00e4a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHKuuxH7LmfEThEFKY3KjLJJncGt9I11ApLwNSBAdIicmC6y4ILpZl1lyCWDicUp1hwicVkbJn3lcRnA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(120, 172, 254);font-size:18px;\">分享画板</span></span></h3>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">对了，画板可以分享给朋友查看哦！！</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">点击右上即可</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016160\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2479108635097493\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"718\" data-width=\"718\" data-height=\"178\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=31ae34a9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHKuuxH7LmfEThEFKY3KjLJCur3QyW1LdchzeXbyvyQibpn2MfDUISThyIUDofsEY1tsA7t7vU9dSA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">这个画板是我分享的，你可以打开看看</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://morisot.ai/share/SMD9Dbh8zX3KNuXopGKOI\" target=\"_blank\">https://morisot.ai/share/SMD9Dbh8zX3KNuXopGKOI</a></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"1720\" data-imgfileid=\"100016169\" data-ratio=\"0.512962962962963\" data-width=\"3352\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=745634e5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHKuuxH7LmfEThEFKY3KjLJynoVK3aQ3O57ibp71WqAc8XDaqn4csUmzjwBhciathXxqEO5x6zUBuZQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(120, 172, 254);font-size:18px;\">假装旅游，朋友圈配图</span></span></h3>\n  <pre><code data-lark-language=\"JSON\" data-wrap=\"true\"><p><span leaf=\"\">“我要发朋友圈，我在深秋的北京旅游”</span></p></code></pre>\n  <p data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"https://sistine-tech.feishu.cn/space/api/box/stream/download/asynccode/?code=MWZhY2Y2ZDZhN2Y1NDQ5YzQ1MDUxMzczN2U3MjU1YTZfUlI5Mk5mR1F1NVdCMEJ1c295M0o3aHVkV20yREI2b1NfVG9rZW46VVlzUWJpM0Jjb1p4cTh4N0NlRWNSVFVhbmpjXzE3NjM5Njg4NDU6MTc2Mzk3MjQ0NV9WNA\" data-src=\"\" align=\"\" alt=\"\" border=\"\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"\" data-s=\"\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" hspace=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" style=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"\" usemap=\"\" vspace=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"3356\" data-height=\"1758\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100016166\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-retry=\"\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016168\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"768\" data-width=\"768\" data-height=\"576\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7cf36f20&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F607DKnuWzlHKuuxH7LmfEThEFKY3KjLJIiavRib40Imymh444NSdKbP3rDSoylGPvU25VABycvXkicl7ic4hcQVPlQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016171\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.524074074074074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"3356\" data-height=\"1758\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cbfa63e9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHKuuxH7LmfEThEFKY3KjLJbrWyicAAlQgsjk1pWpM5YRVibkzVmAHqzcrIERuO5Nib7QQoeX6ns76Kw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(120, 172, 254);font-size:18px;\">给狗子穿衣服</span></span></h3>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"1620\" data-imgfileid=\"100016167\" data-ratio=\"0.6027777777777777\" data-width=\"2688\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f178c30d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHKuuxH7LmfEThEFKY3KjLJjfKWicuHDYRddDZrzVm6XNsqsHeVe1CmhVDxvOia5LjQzkOM56pkicJew%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(120, 172, 254);font-size:18px;\">甚至可以不要参考图，直接从模糊的idea开始</span></span></h3>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">我们甚至可以不传参考图，直接从模糊的场景开始描述，仍然能得到</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">一墙风格统一的图。</span></strong></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">例如：</span></p>\n  <pre><code data-lark-language=\"JSON\" data-wrap=\"true\"><p><span leaf=\"\">“我心情有点emo，想发个朋友圈，给我配图”</span></p></code></pre>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016170\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5287037037037037\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"3390\" data-height=\"1792\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e716f3a8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHKuuxH7LmfEThEFKY3KjLJdXwg5qXzzh9UHEJMiamI4ktWpzk6rtaM0ECsRnImRnxicxOvWOr2p9FQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);font-size:24px;\">请你帮忙 🙏</span></span></h3>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">写到这里，你大概已经知道 Morisot 是干嘛的了。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">接下来，我想正式邀请你，来当这块 AI 画图板的「联合产品经理」。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">你可以这样帮我：</span></p>\n  <ol class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" start=\"1\">\n   <li style=\"text-align:left;\">\n    <p><strong><span leaf=\"\">随便玩一玩，帮我找 bug / 不爽之处</span></strong></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"text-align:left;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">装修、朋友圈、给狗子穿衣服、涂鸦变大作……你怎么用都行。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"text-align:left;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">只要哪儿觉得别扭、慢、看不懂，欢迎在公众号留言，或者微信戳我说一声。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">只要是认真反馈，用完积分跟我说，我给你加。</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <ol class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" start=\"2\">\n   <li style=\"text-align:left;\">\n    <p><strong><span leaf=\"\">帮我挖掘「特别对味」的使用场景</span></strong></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"text-align:left;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">比如你发现了一个很好玩的用法：</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"text-align:left;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">给老板做方案对比</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"text-align:left;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">给孩子做故事插画</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"text-align:left;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">给对象做生日贺卡……</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <li style=\"text-align:left;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">都欢迎告诉我，我会在后面整理一个「Morisot 使用场景合集」，把你的点子写进去。</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <ol class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" start=\"3\">\n   <li style=\"text-align:left;\">\n    <p><strong><span leaf=\"\">如果你是做内容 / 自媒体的</span></strong></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"text-align:left;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">想想：如果是你来向读者推荐 Morisot，你会从哪个角度讲？</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"text-align:left;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">你可以随便写一篇体验、教程、吐槽都行，发给我看。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"text-align:left;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">之后我会在产品更新里，挑一些优质内容挂上署名和链接。</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <ol class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" start=\"4\">\n   <li style=\"text-align:left;\">\n    <p><strong><span leaf=\"\">分享你的画板 / 作品给我</span></strong></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"text-align:left;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">用 Morisot 画完图后，点右上角就能分享画板链接。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"text-align:left;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">你可以发给朋友，也可以丢给我。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"text-align:left;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">后面我会做一个「用户作品展墙」，把大家好看的图和奇怪的点子都挂上去。</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">你现在就可以做一件小事：</span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\">打开&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">Morisot</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;👉 <a href=\"https://morisot.ai\" target=\"_blank\">https://morisot.ai</a> &nbsp;随便丢一张图进去，或者写一句模糊的想法， &nbsp;看看它给你的第一堵「好图之墙」， &nbsp;然后在评论区告诉我：</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;你第一反应，想拿它来干嘛？</span></strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">谢谢你帮我一起把 Morisot 养大。</span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Morisot 是一款无需 Prompt 即可 AI 绘画的产品，通过“看图选择-自然语言修改”的流程，降低用户创作门槛，解决用户难以用语言准确描述需求的问题。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Morisot 是一款无需 Prompt 即可 AI 绘画的产品，通过“看图选择-自然语言修改”的流程，降低用户创作门槛，解决用户难以用语言准确描述需求的问题。",
  "summary": "文章介绍了作者刘小排开发的新产品 Morisot，一款旨在解决用户在 AI 绘画中难以准确描述 Prompt 痛点的工具。作者通过亲身经历（手机输入法皮肤设计）阐述观点：人类创作常始于“看”而非“描述”，即“I know it when I see it”。Morisot 的核心功能是用户只需输入模糊想法，系统便能快速生成一墙风格各异的图像供用户选择，再通过自然语言进行迭代修改。文章展示了装修效果图、朋友圈配图等多种应用案例，并邀请读者作为“联合产品经理”参与产品测试、反馈 Bug、挖掘使用场景，并分享作品，旨在共同打磨和推广产品。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "传统 AI 绘画工具过度依赖复杂 Prompt，限制了大多数不善语言表达的用户的创作。",
      "explanation": "大部分用户难以用精确语言描述需求，导致 AIGC 工具门槛高，无法满足“说不清”用户的创作需求，造成了创作体验上的障碍。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Morisot 通过“先看后选再改”的创作流程，有效降低 AI 绘画门槛，提升用户体验。",
      "explanation": "产品设计符合人类“I know it when I see it”的直觉，通过快速生成多样化图像供用户选择，再以自然语言迭代修改，极大简化了创作过程。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Morisot 产品设计体现了以用户为中心的理念，注重解决实际痛点和交互创新。",
      "explanation": "作者从自身痛点出发，设计出更符合非专业用户习惯的 AI 绘画交互方式，对 AI 产品设计具有借鉴意义，有望拓展 AIGC 应用边界。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "人类创作不是从 Prompt 开始的，是从眼睛开始的。",
    "我不是不知道自己要什么，我只是没办法用语言先把它描述出来。",
    "绝大多数创作，都不是从'描述'开始的，是从'看'开始的。",
    "你可能说不清你要什么图，但你看到的时候，就知道哪张对。",
    "平凡的我们，创作流程应该是 ： 说不清 → 先看一墙图 → 指一指喜欢的 → 再改一改"
  ],
